@page "/installation"
@rendermode InteractiveServer

<PageTitle>Installation - MudQuillEditor</PageTitle>

<div class="mb-6">
    <MudText Typo="Typo.h3" GutterBottom="true">Installation Guide</MudText>
    <MudText Typo="Typo.subtitle1">Get MudQuillEditor up and running in your Blazor project</MudText>
</div>

<MudText Typo="Typo.h5" GutterBottom="true" Class="mt-6">Step 1: Add NuGet Package</MudText>
<MudPaper Class="pa-4 mb-4">
    <MudText Typo="Typo.body2" Class="mb-3">Install the MudQuillEditor package from NuGet:</MudText>
    <pre style="background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px;border-radius:4px;border-left:4px solid #2196F3;"><code>dotnet add package TheNerdCollective.MudQuillEditor</code></pre>
</MudPaper>

<MudText Typo="Typo.h5" GutterBottom="true" Class="mt-6">Step 2: Add Script Reference</MudText>
<MudPaper Class="pa-4 mb-4">
    <MudText Typo="Typo.body2" Class="mb-3">In your <code>App.razor</code>, add the MudQuillEditor script reference before the Blazor runtime script:</MudText>
    <pre style="background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px;border-radius:4px;border-left:4px solid #2196F3;"><code>&lt;script src="_content/TheNerdCollective.MudQuillEditor/js/mudquilleditor.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
&lt;script src="_framework/blazor.server.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</code></pre>
    
    <MudAlert Class="mt-3" Severity="Severity.Info">
        <strong>Requirements:</strong> MudBlazor must be installed and configured. MudQuillEditor automatically loads Quill CSS/JS from CDN and handles all dependencies.
    </MudAlert>
</MudPaper>

<MudText Typo="Typo.h5" GutterBottom="true" Class="mt-6">Step 3: Use the Component</MudText>
<MudPaper Class="pa-4 mb-4">
    <MudText Typo="Typo.body2" Class="mb-3">Bind the component to a property and optionally configure height and other options:</MudText>
    <pre style="background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px;border-radius:4px;border-left:4px solid #4CAF50;"><code>&lt;MudQuillEditor @@bind-Value="HtmlContent" 
               MinHeight="150px" 
               MaxHeight="300px"
               Placeholder="Enter text here..." /&gt;

@@code {{
    private string HtmlContent = "&lt;p&gt;Hello&lt;/p&gt;";
}}</code></pre>
</MudPaper>

